                    </ul>
                    <li>Text Editor Development: </li>
                    <ul>
                        <li>A Vim or VSCode-like editor</li>
                    </ul>
                    <li>Penetration Testing: </li>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Being able to write programs to test for vulnerabilities</li>
                    </ul>
