                <ul>
                    <li>Zig: A general purpose language to build robust, optimal and reusable programs.</li>
                    <li>Rust: A language built to deliver high performance applications with guaranteed memory/thread safety. </li>
                    <li>C: A general purpose language to build high performance programs</li>
